# =============================================================
# WHITELIST-ONLY GITIGNORE — blocks everything except doc files
# =============================================================
# This repo is PUBLIC. Only documentation files should exist here.
# If you accidentally copy code or secrets, this gitignore prevents
# them from being staged by `git add .`

# Block EVERYTHING by default
*

# Allow directory traversal (required for nested folders to work)
!*/

# Allow only documentation file types
!*.mdx
!*.json
!*.png
!*.svg
!*.ico
!.gitignore

# Explicitly block dangerous file types (defense in depth)
# These override the whitelist above as an extra safety net
*.py
*.pyc
*.ts
*.tsx
*.js
*.jsx
*.env
*.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.sql
*.sh
*.bash
*.zsh
*.yaml
*.yml
*.toml
*.cfg
*.ini
*.log
*.csv
*.db
*.sqlite
*.pickle
*.pkl
*.tar
*.gz
*.zip
requirements.txt
package.json
package-lock.json
Dockerfile
docker-compose*
CLAUDE.md
README.md
DEPLOYMENT.md
*.service-account*.json
*firebase*.json
